skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: baby names
des:
This skill is trying to help you by given some creative first names from all around the world.

So if you're searching a first name for you baby or even pet. Then this might be exactly what you're seeking.

Here you've got the possibility to let alexa suggest names for you randomly. Our database contains over 36000 first names from all around the world which will be randomly picked for you.

To get a first name suggestion say:
"Alexa, start baby names"
"Alexa, ask baby names for a boy name"
"Alexa, ask baby names for a girl name"

We hope you enjoy this skill and find what you're searching for.
And of course, congratulations for your baby or pet!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
